/**
 * SFX Engine
 *
 * Plays WAV sound effects for game events using Web Audio API.
 * - Default event → file mappings (customizable via Sound Designer dev panel)
 * - Mappings persisted to localStorage as `soundEventMap`
 * - Previewing any file is supported via previewSfx()
 */

